l": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-6cb46677086aa5265fb42276cfd35ae9_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/520557451"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIz4rklqnzzN42EAMaCDc3OTYxMDkxINPolpEGMAA4QEAiaAByCTUyMDU1NzQ1MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1646882031.5784864", "card_id": "Q_520733448", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 88}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "现在高二了，因为完全学不懂，也不想学了非常的厌学，不想读书了，我该怎么办?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/520733448"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIz4rklqnzzN42EAMaCDc4MDAwMjk2ILDdm5EGMAE4YUAjaAByCTUyMDczMzQ0OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1646882031.5788152", "card_id": "Q_520818243", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 57}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "初中混日子过的，初三下学期努力还来得及吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "已经到初三下学期了，而我完全就是混日子过的，就剩 100 多天，努力还来得及吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a822bb5f51eb27666e48d2fa337525b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/520818243"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIz4rklqnzzN42EAMaCDc4MDE5MTI2INfVnZEGMAE4OUAkaAByCTUyMDgxODI0M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1646882031.5793364", "card_id": "Q_520950759", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人大代表建议将「盲驾」行为视为「危险驾驶」并进行严厉查处，你是否支持？你还有哪些交通方面的建议？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "开车时玩手机发消息，不仅分散驾驶员的注意力，而且可能在短时间内处于「盲驾」。「盲驾」是指在驾驶中玩弄手机和手持终端的相关行为。「『盲驾’实际上比』醉驾’更具危险性。」全国人大代表、全国道德模范张青彬在接受采访时表示。对此，在今年全国两会期间，张青彬建议将「盲驾」行为视为「危险驾驶」并进行严厉查处。 《中华人民共和国道路交通安全法实施条例 (2017 修订)》第六十二条规定：驾驶机动车不得有「拨打接听手持电话、观看电视等妨碍安全驾驶的行为」，但没有将「盲驾」的有关表述列入。 目前，开车「低头族」越来越多。张青彬认为，当驾驶员低头看手机时, 车辆实际上处于无人驾驶的状态, 潜在的危险性非常大。「‘盲驾’必须引起社会、特别是交通安全部门的高度重视。」张青彬说道。 今年全国两会期间，张青彬建议有关部门能够以典型案例为基础进行统计调查，研究重大交通事故中「盲驾」的比例，摸清底数。另外，有关部门还可以专门组织力量从社会学、法学、运动学等多角度、多方面开展研究。 针对「盲驾」行为的立法方面，张青彬建议参照「醉驾」入法，为严格查处「盲驾」行为提供法律依据。如何对「盲驾」行为进行取证？张青彬建议可以通过驾驶员或其同乘人的口供、监控录像、行车记录仪等途径获取。 除此之外，张青彬还建议公安部、交管部等有关部门尽快开展严厉查处「盲驾」行为的专项行动并修改、完善相关的规章。张青彬代表：建议将「盲驾」行为视为「危险驾驶」并进行严厉查处"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/520950759"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIz4rklqnzzN42EAMaCDc4MDQ4NjA1IN/CoZEGMAA4L0AlaAByCTUyMDk1MDc1OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1646882031.5803123", "card_id": "Q_520496524", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何正视自己的平庸?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c8404780221df2573db3b9d4041d2c98_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/520496524"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIz4rklqnzzN42EAMaCDc3OTQ3NTUwIMTDlZEGMAA4UUAmaAByCTUyMDQ5NjUyNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1646882031.5806973", "card_id": "Q_496951219", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何以「天帝砍了吾的魔角」为题写个故事?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "没人尴尬了，我虐的甜的都 ok 啊"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/496951219"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIz4rklqnzzN42EAMaCDcyNzE0OTMwILKm